    "alignment": "大多数矮人守序，坚信秩序井然的社会带来的好处。他们也倾向于善良，具有强烈的公平意识，并相信每个人都应分享正义秩序的利益。",
    "alignment_en": "Most dwarves are lawful, believing firmly in the benefits of a well-ordered society. They tend toward good as well, with a strong sense of fair play and a belief that everyone deserves to share in the benefits of a just order.",
    "age": "矮人的成熟速度与人类相同，但在50岁之前都被认为是年轻人。平均而言，他们能活大约350年。",
    "age_en": "Dwarves mature at the same rate as humans, but they're considered young until they reach the age of 50. On average, they live about 350 years.",
    "size": "中型",
    "size_en": "Medium",
    "size_description": "矮人身高在4到5英尺之间，平均体重约150磅。你的体型为中型。",
    "size_description_en": "Dwarves stand between 4 and 5 feet tall and average about 150 pounds. Your size is Medium.",
