    "language_desc": "你能说、读、写通用语和矮人语。矮人语充满了硬辅音和喉音，这些特征会在矮人说其他语言时流露出来。",
    "language_desc_en": "You can speak, read, and write Common and Dwarvish. Dwarvish is full of hard consonants and guttural sounds, and those characteristics spill over into whatever other language a dwarf might speak.",
