    "age": "虽然精灵大约在与人类相同的年龄达到生理成熟，但精灵对成年的理解超越了生理成长，涵盖了 worldly experience。精灵通常在100岁左右宣称成年并使用成年名字，可以活到750岁。",
    "age_en": "Although elves reach physical maturity at about the same age as humans, the elven understanding of adulthood goes beyond physical growth to encompass worldly experience. An elf typically claims adulthood and an adult name around the age of 100 and can live to be 750 years old.",
    "alignment": "精灵热爱自由、多样性和自我表达，因此他们强烈倾向于混乱的温和方面。他们珍视并保护自己和他人的自由，他们通常是善良的。",
    "alignment_en": "Elves love freedom, variety, and self-expression, so they lean strongly toward the gentler aspects of chaos. They value and protect others' freedom as well as their own, and they are more often good than not.",
    "size": "中型",
    "size_en": "Medium",
    "size_description": "精灵身高从不到5英尺到超过6英尺不等，身材苗条。你的体型为中型。",
    "size_description_en": "Elves range from under 5 to over 6 feet tall and have slender builds. Your size is Medium.",
    "languages": [
      {
        "index": "common",
        "name": "通用语",
        "name_en": "Common",
        "url": "/api/2014/languages/common"
      },
      {
