        "name": "精灵语",
        "name_en": "Elvish",
        "url": "/api/2014/languages/elvish"
      }
    ],
    "language_desc": "你能说、读、写通用语和精灵语。精灵语流畅，带有微妙的语调和复杂的语法。精灵文学丰富多样，他们的歌曲和诗歌在其他种族中享有盛名。许多吟游诗人学习他们的语言，以便将精灵民谣添加到他们的曲目中。",
    "language_desc_en": "You can speak, read, and write Common and Elvish. Elvish is fluid, with subtle intonations and intricate grammar. Elven literature is rich and varied, and their songs and poems are famous among other races. Many bards learn their language so they can add Elvish ballads to their repertoires.",
