    "age": "半身人在20岁时成年，通常能活到第二个世纪的中期。",
    "age_en": "A halfling reaches adulthood at the age of 20 and generally lives into the middle of his or her second century.",
    "alignment": "大多数半身人是守序善良的。作为规则，他们心地善良，憎恨看到别人痛苦，对压迫没有容忍度。他们也非常有序和传统，严重依赖社区的支持和他们古老方式的安慰。",
    "alignment_en": "Most halflings are lawful good. As a rule, they are good-hearted and kind, hate to see others in pain, and have no tolerance for oppression. They are also very orderly and traditional, leaning heavily on the support of their community and the comfort of their old ways.",
    "size": "小型",
    "size_en": "Small",
    "size_description": "半身人平均身高约3英尺，体重约40磅。你的体型为小型。",
    "size_description_en": "Halflings average about 3 feet tall and weigh about 40 pounds. Your size is Small.",
    "languages": [
      {
        "index": "common",
        "name": "通用语",
        "name_en": "Common",
        "url": "/api/2014/languages/common"
      },
      {
        "index": "halfling",
        "name": "半身人语",
        "name_en": "Halfling",
        "url": "/api/2014/languages/halfling"
      }
    ],
    "language_desc": "你能说、读、写通用语和半身人语。半身人语不是秘密，但半身人不愿与他人分享。他们很少书写，因此没有丰富的文学作品。然而，他们的口头传统非常强大。几乎所有半身人都说通用语，以便与他们居住或旅行经过的土地上的人交流。",
    "language_desc_en": "You can speak, read, and write Common and Halfling. The Halfling language isn't secret, but halflings are loath to share it with others. They write very little, so they don't have a rich body of literature. Their oral tradition, however, is very strong. Almost all halflings speak Common to converse with the people in whose lands they dwell or through which they are traveling.",
    "traits": [
